extendedInfo.description: Do your dare to test if you are healthy by scanning your fingerprint without going  to see the doctor?Yes, of course.It can't really check your body by only scanning the fingerprint.If you really feel uncomfortable,hurry to go to hospital.Don't rely on the FAKE app.It is only designed for playing jokes on your friends.This app Health Fingerprint Testing is very simple to use.After downloading it to your phone,enter the main page of the app.It will tell you to scan your fingerprint.Place your finger on the scanning area .Make sure enough time to hold the design until it vibrates.Otherwise,it doesn't work.If succeed to scan the fingerprint,the sampling value will appear.After analyzing,it will connect to gene database automatically.Last,you will know you are healthy or not.Besides,if you still don't know how to test,you can read some directions in the app.Wanna to find the hidden secrets on the fingerprint?Prank your friends and make them believe you take the "DOCTOR" with you anywhere anytime.+++++++++++++++++++++++++Must Read+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++1.This app is brought to you totally free.However,we have opted to use icon ads or notification ads to beable to keep creating more free apps for you.2.Fake app for pranks.+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++Fingerprint records often contain impressions from the pad on the last joint of fingers and thumbs, although fingerprint cards also typically record portions of lower joint areas of the fingers.
